text: [[!Tishana Voice]]

Topical, I just wrote about this for my first Commanding Respect article. I used to play Sunder in Patron of the Moon. It wasn't even the douchiest of win conditions, but I felt like a *terrible* human being after resolving it. All of my opponents returned their lands to their hands, and their hands to their decks, and their decks to their deckboxes, and their deckboxes to their bags...
